 a valuable asset to the team and would highly recommend her to any team should she decide to progress further in her career.", "recommendations/0/name": "Effie Marcella Masudal", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Certified Hospitality Trainer | Learning and Development | Quality Improvement", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/effie-marcella-masudal-a27654126/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB8QXb8Bt5DqEAZw9xsk89vdXjyiI27LdJM", "recommendations/1/context": "Khairil Hafez managed Mizi directly", "recommendations/1/date": "February 18, 2021", "recommendations/1/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Chef Mizi in 2019 during the pre-opening of Desa Selatan Resort (Southern Village Resort) in Pengerang. He successfully led the Kitchen team in ensuring that all essential kitchen operation matters were perfectly up and running to accept our first batch of long-stay guests from PRPC. Throughout his time there he ensured that the quality of food was always consistent and that our guests were always satisfied with their meals. He was also meticulous in ensuring that food costs and operational costs were very well managed without having to sacrifice quality. ", "recommendations/1/name": "Mizi S.", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Certified Chef and Halal Advisor...Open to new challange.", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/roshamizi-saad-424221103/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABox8xwB3K4Ik-Bq8g07kjbCulyrmumDsWk", "recommendations/2/context": "Khairil Hafez managed Yainne directly", "recommendations/2/date": "January 6, 2021", "recommendations/2/description": "I had the pleasure of getting to know and working with Yainne since 2016. As an Executive Assistant she was a gem to work with and provided plenty of support to the entire team. Easy-going and detail oriented, she worked well with all levels of staff in every department. Being the go-to person between the Executive Office and other departments, as well as Owner's office, she displayed great communication and kept things organized and ensured that the property's administration side ran smoothly. As a someone with many talents, besides her administrative duties, she was also readily available and willing to assist in operations when required. Overall a great person to be with and an asset to any organization.", "recommendations/2/name": "Yainne Rais", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "HR people and business intergrations.. Develop, Grow, Risk and Chances are keys of togetherness..", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yainne-rais-65344614a/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACQEQB8B7fzNT27oOsWhtyenNFRV7dfHx5w", "recommendations/3/context": "Khairil Hafez worked with Cheryl on the same team", "recommendations/3/date": "November 6, 2020", "recommendations/3/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Cheryl on two occasions, first being with Tune Hotels and the second at Impiana. Cheryl is definitely the best at what she does and has helped me tremendously in successfully managing and yielding revenue to ensure highest profitability as possible in both hotels that I have overseen. Her analytical skills and ability to forecast is top class. Given the opportunity I would definitely work with Cheryl again. ", "recommendations/3/name": "Cheryl W.", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Payments | Revenue Analyst | BD", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/cherylwsw/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAwb4DgB4mQNLIPFRwPk2srUo_IEj_1Xdys", "recommendations/4/context": "Khairil Hafez reported directly to Anwar", "recommendations/4/date": "November 6, 2020", "recommendations/4/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Anwar for several years at Tune Hotels. Being the elder statesman overseeing the team of young Hotel Managers, Anwar was more than just a boss or a leader. He was a father figure and a mentor who’s words of wisdom and experience guided not only in regards to my work and career at the time but also in life. He encouraged me to take risks and step out of my comfort zone in order to reach greater heights. ", "recommendations/4/name": "Anwar Jumabhoy", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Expert on \"Entrepreneurial Practices\" - Learn how companies adopt entrepreneurial practices to compete in a VUCA world, compete with startups & motivate talent. You don't have to start a business to be \"entrepreneurial\".", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/anwarjumabhoy/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADAch0BxEEQNuHAiSuiVSqZa4FAfZDq4Sg", "recommendations/5/date": "August 11, 2020", "recommendations/5/description": "I have had the pleasure of knowing Mawarid since college. He is possesses a unique and likeable character. Very friendly and always has a very positive outlook to everything be it in life or work. He is very hardworking and is a very determined person with excellent interpersonal skills. His passion in what he does is clearly demonstrated in the work he does and in his career achievements. Overall I would recommend Mawarid for any organization as he would be a great asset to any team. ", "recommendations/5/name": "Mawarid Zamzam", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "Staff Affairs | Leadership & Capability Devp. | Stakeholder Management | Corporate Affairs “Multi-talented professional, harnessing years of experience and knowledge to drive impactful change and foster innovation.”", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mawarid-zamzam-664a51129/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB-oJ2wBIMJa7RhyQR2DpTow1wKCdlxdw7o", "recommendations/6/context": "Khairil Hafez managed Muhammad Azim directly", "recommendations/6/date": "September 21, 2019", "recommendations/6/description": "I have known Muhammad Azim for the past 4 years and have worked with him in 2 different properties. It was his ability to demonstrate good leadership even at a young age that decided to take him with me from Somerset Medini Iskandar to Lakeview Terrace Resort. In both properties he has shown maturity in his leadership by leading and influencing teams consisting of personnel who were much older than him. The knowledge and experience he has gained during his time in Australia has certainly developed him into a talented and upcoming leader for the future. ", "recommendations/6/name": "Muhammad Azim abd Jabar", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Assistant Director of Safety and Security at Sunway International Hotels & Resorts", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/muhammad-azim-abd-jabar-71916313b/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACIEOkUBSiSuENTvaghBb4QiECDwmxrCzls", "recommendations/7/context": "Susan was senior to Khairil Hafez but didn't manage Khairil Hafez directly", "recommendations/7/date": "October 23, 2017", "recommendations/7/description": "Susan and I worked together at The Ascott Limited. I thoroughly enjoyed my time working with Susan, and came to know her as a truly valuable asset to absolutely any team. My first impression of her the first time we met was that she is friendly with a bubbly and warm personality, honest, dependable, and incredibly hard-working. Beyond that, she is an impressive HR practitioner  who is always driven.\n\nHer knowledge and expertise in Human Resource Management was a huge advantage to our team. Along with her undeniable talent, Susan has always been an absolute joy to work with. She is a true team player, and always manages to foster positive discussions and bring the best out of other employees.\n\nWithout a doubt, I confidently recommend Susan if you are in need of someone to lead your HR. As a dedicated and knowledgeable leader and an all-around great person, I know that she will be a beneficial addition to any team.", "recommendations/7/name": "Susan Abdullah Crone", "recommendations/7/subtitle": "Professional Luxury Hotelier | People & Culture Strategist | Talent Acquisition Specialist | Employee Engagement Advocate | Diversity & Inclusion Champion", "recommendations/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/susan-abdullahcrone/", "recommendations/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALniYUB-xVdPw447QQuoOm4nX353tct_3M", "recommendations/8/context": "Khairil Hafez worked with Sheikh Mohamed Iqbal  on the same team", "recommendations/8/date": "June 12, 2015", "recommendations/8/description": "I have had the pleasure to work with Sheikh Iqbal for 2 years at Tune Hotels. I can honestly say that when it comes to building and facilities maintenance he is the best at what he does. As the head of maintenance Sheikh Iqbal has an eye for detail and the forward vision to ensure that preventive maintenance programs are effectively carried. He has also been a great leader especially to his team of maintenance technicians and has been highly regarded. I look forward to be able to work together with him again in the future.", "recommendations/8/name": "Sheikh Mohamed Iqbal  Sheikh Mohamed Zakaria", "recommendations/8/subtitle": "Product & Innovation Manager | Smart Cities | Digital Transformation | Open to Opportunities in Saudi Arabia & UAE", "recommendations/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sheikhmohamediqbal/", "recommendations/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABXBRo8B-pd_jQ3Tlr7NYXFFucqO0hUEeMU", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "February 5, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "I had the opportunity to work under Khairil Hafez for a good 3 years with him as our Resident Manager in Somerset Medini. \n\nWe were in the pre opening team and with his democratic leadership style, I not only grew but had so much fun working with the team! \nKhairil Hafez is not only focused, cultivate great teamspirit amongst the staff, but also has always shown high interest and continuous support in all areas of the hotel including Training! \n\nI will recommend Hafez without any hesitation to any establishment.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Effie Marcella Masudal", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Certified Hospitality Trainer | Learning and Development | Quality Improvement", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/effie-marcella-masudal-a27654126/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB8QXb8Bt5DqEAZw9xsk89vdXjyiI27LdJM", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Yainne reported directly to Khairil Hafez", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "January 6, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I have worked directly with Hafez during the several years that he has served as Residence Manager. Excellent in his role and exhibiting high standards for quality. Hafez possesses the ultimate \"can do\" attitude with the team with a positive energy and a smile. His upbeat personality and engaging personal style enable him to interact effectively with not only guest or supplier but all level of staff. Not only he guides, he allows to pursue their specialities that he sees towards all his staff to ensure they can develop. Thus, he provides immediate gratitude when it had impacted positively in the organisation. Theres always work life balance. All the intangibles that lead to success without stress in the workplace are in order with Hafez. There will be no unpleasant surprises with his leads.. Awesome boss! \n", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Yainne Rais", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "HR people and business intergrations.. Develop, Grow, Risk and Chances are keys of togetherness..", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yainne-rais-65344614a/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACQEQB8B7fzNT27oOsWhtyenNFRV7dfHx5w", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Cheryl worked with Khairil Hafez on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "November 6, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "It has been a pleasure working with Hafez during my tenureship with two different companies, an individual whom mentors and guides his team very well. With vast experience Hafez have, every challenge that he faces would be resolved and I am always impressed on how he does these even with on-going crisis. \n\nHis positive vibes and energy brings his team intact and synergised. It's without any hesitation, that I would recommend Hafez in any workforce, as it's rare to have a GM with a personality and experiences like him. ", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Cheryl W.", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Payments | Revenue Analyst | BD", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/cherylwsw/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAwb4DgB4mQNLIPFRwPk2srUo_IEj_1Xdys", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Anwar worked with Khairil Hafez on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "November 6, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Hafez over several years. It did not take long for me to recognise his potential, willingness to take on bigger roles and his ability to lead a team. He stepped out of his comfort zone in Kota Kinabalu to take on new roles. He left at a moment's notice to stand in for a manager at Tune Edinburgh, who had fallen ill. Then took on new Hotel Manager roles at other hotels in Tune Group. I have followed his progress since leaving, always bringing a customer focus and a commitment to support his team.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Anwar Jumabhoy", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Expert on \"Entrepreneurial Practices\" - Learn how companies adopt entrepreneurial practices to compete in a VUCA world, compete with startups & motivate talent. You don't have to start a business to be \"entrepreneurial\".", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/anwarjumabhoy/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADAch0BxEEQNuHAiSuiVSqZa4FAfZDq4Sg", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "August 11, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "We've known each other for over 26 years. Hafez and I went to the same university, so I had the privilege of taking a few classes with him and seeing how smart he was. He is an excellent learner, and his experience of hospitality is very extensive. His ability to concentrate helped him become the hospitality specialist that he is now.\n\nHis positive attitude astounds me and he's going to be my person when I need advice in the field of hospitality and management. Hafez is highly applied and aims at high-quality work. Hafez is creative, knowledgeable, has outstanding communication skills and ready to help if you need it. He's the kind of person who does something for the benefit of the group. Hafez is a great professional to have, and a fine fellow!", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Mawarid Zamzam", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Staff Affairs | Leadership & Capability Devp. | Stakeholder Management | Corporate Affairs “Multi-talented professional, harnessing years of experience and knowledge to drive impactful change and foster innovation.”", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mawarid-zamzam-664a51129/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB-oJ2wBIMJa7RhyQR2DpTow1wKCdlxdw7o", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Muhammad Azim reported directly to Khairil Hafez", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "September 21, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "I have known Mr. Khairil Hafez for the past 4 years and have worked with him in 2 different properties. Few people have the opportunity to report to a manager who is also a coach and mentor, but I did when I worked for Mr. Hafez. I had the pleasure of working with Mr. Hafez. I was always in awe of Mr. Hafez’s ability to manage a hotel, resort and get people on board with ideas. Even people who were initially on completely different pages. No matter how tense a meeting, Mr. Hafez made sure everyone left with a smile. Mr. Hafez would be an asset to any company.", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Muhammad Azim abd Jabar", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "Assistant Director of Safety and Security at Sunway International Hotels & Resorts", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/muhammad-azim-abd-jabar-71916313b/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACIEOkUBSiSuENTvaghBb4QiECDwmxrCzls", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Dennis worked with Khairil Hafez on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "October 27, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "Hafez was a colleague of mine during my time with Tune Hotels Sdn Bhd.  He's very passionate about the hospitality industry and his calm and approachable demeanour makes him a great leader too.  He's great with human development and believe that staffs are the most important asset in any organisation. A very professional and respected figure at work but a great friend after work, and he's a great cook too. ", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Dennis Cheng, CHA®", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "Hospitality Management", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/dennis-cheng1973/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAV2HDIB4EsZikpI24dhzD_IkDt0m1zECDM", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Sheikh Mohamed Iqbal  worked with Khairil Hafez on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "September 21, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "I thoroughly enjoyed my time working with Kharil Hafez, and came to know him as a truly valuable asset to absolutely any team. He is honest, dependable, and incredibly hard-working. Beyond that, he is an impressive asset to any establishment who is always a result oriented person, being there when he is needed and delivering as what he is required.\n\nHis knowledge and expertise was a huge advantage to our entire establishment and team. He put this skillset to work i